### create artical
POST http://localhost:4000/author-api/article
Content-Type: application/json

{
     "author":"69ae3cdd094522c71d2549b8",
     "title":"Python",
     "category":"Course",
     "content":"this is Python article"
}

### read artical
GET http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles/69ae3cdd094522c71d2549b8


### update the artical
PUT http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
     "author":"69ae3cdd094522c71d2549b8",
     "articleId":"69ae772231b587604534d787",
     "title":"Java",
     "category":"programming",
     "content":"updated content"
}
### soft delete the article

PATCH  http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles/69ae772231b587604534d787
Content-Type: application/json

{
     "isArticleActive":true
}

###logout
GET http://localhost:4000/common-api/logout


### get article by user
GET http://localhost:4000/user-api/article

### add comment to article

PUT http://localhost:4000/user-api/articleComment 
Content-Type: application/json

{
     "user":"69ae3c3c094522c71d2549b6",
     "articleId":"69ae772231b587604534d787",
     "comment":"Excellent"
}


